{"tid":1946711,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣算唔算便秘","createTime":"2020-03-27T19:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T10:51:20.000Z","uid":309220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f066e5f918b5b5eea76b9c9deb0910cad2c8f68","tid":1946711,"uid":309220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T19:52:41.000Z","msg":"由於本人實在接受唔到喺屋企以外嘅地方去大，除非真係忍唔到，一般都會忍到返屋企先去，但係通常返到屋企就唔急，所以兩三日先屙一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過屙得好暢順，一坐就去到。<br />\n但係近排因為唔洗返學校 好少出街，基本上日日都有得去。不過有時要坐兩三次先去到，屙得好唔順暢，仲要屙得好少，完全冇平時屙屎嘅暢快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁樣算唔算便秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a29780262897ea0d03a1a3801cae5511765117","tid":1946711,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"A little bit"},{"pid":"7e01d5456bd76fbb12c5e2eeb671251df224db86","tid":1946711,"uid":99879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9777a01e78f2a82f00f778d0547f3844fc8ee515","tid":1946711,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e01d5456bd76fbb12c5e2eeb671251df224db86","tid":1946711,"uid":99879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"成個月無屎all,會谷到個人好臭，老細會炒左你<br />\n（拉）"},{"pid":"f6ce84b9ff96e84eae27cbdbd32fd4874eb6a0f9","tid":1946711,"uid":99879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"920d0c0f6a18cf0095ed110de0958432a03508cf","tid":1946711,"uid":309220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e01d5456bd76fbb12c5e2eeb671251df224db86","tid":1946711,"uid":99879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"成個月<img src=\"/assets/